--------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |TOP-N SORT          |                    |1       |17          |
|1 |â””â”€HASH JOIN         |                    |1       |17          |
|2 |  â”śâ”€TABLE RANGE SCAN|dc(ind_user_type_id)|1       |8           |
|3 |  â””â”€TABLE RANGE SCAN|logs(ind_shop_id)   |1       |9           |
====================================================================
